Dialogue: 99,0:00:05.73,0:00:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,O que é esse barulho?
Dialogue: 99,0:00:19.16,0:00:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sra. Ryu...?
Dialogue: 99,0:00:21.54,0:00:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Não de novo.
Dialogue: 99,0:00:23.25,0:00:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,É exatamente o mesmo.
Dialogue: 99,0:00:24.96,0:00:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Essa coisa... ela está vindo...
Dialogue: 99,0:00:28.76,0:00:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Alise...
Dialogue: 99,0:00:33.43,0:00:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ei, então...
Dialogue: 99,0:00:35.39,0:00:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuja.
Dialogue: 99,0:00:36.47,0:00:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 99,0:00:37.52,0:00:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Você tem que fugir!
Dialogue: 99,0:00:39.14,0:00:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Corra e se afaste!
Dialogue: 99,0:00:40.39,0:00:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Pelo menos você tem que escapar! Saia daqui!
Dialogue: 99,0:00:42.40,0:00:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Tem pressa!
Dialogue: 99,0:00:46.65,0:00:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Tarde demais!
Dialogue: 99,0:00:48.11,0:00:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Estamos na presença do desespero!
Dialogue: 99,0:00:50.57,0:00:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim! Vamos lá!
Dialogue: 99,0:00:51.99,0:00:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mostre-se para todos!
Dialogue: 99,0:00:53.91,0:00:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mais uma vez! Deixe-nos ver de perto!
Dialogue: 99,0:01:04.42,0:01:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Uma grande tragédia... se aproxima.
Dialogue: 99,0:01:15.47,0:01:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tenha cuidado.
Dialogue: 99,0:01:17.18,0:01:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}É um banquete de tragédia.
